editar arquivo ssl

linux:~# vim /etc/apache2/sites-available/ssl

NameVirtualHost *:443
<VirtualHost *:443>
ServerAdmin webmaster@localhost
SSLEngine On
SSLCertificateFile /etc/apache2/ssl/apache.pem
DocumentRoot /var/www/
 

Depois execute na console:
linux:~# a2ensite ssl
linux:~# /etc/init.d/apache2 force-reload

</pre>";

